OL,6,CStage B
OL,8,GAstronauts experience cognitive
OL,9,Gimpairment, bone loss, muscle
OL,10,Gdeterioration, depression, and
OL,11,Gcontinence challenges. Nobody calls it
OL,12,Gfailure. Space stays aspirational on
OL,13,Gpurpose. The language, the
OL,14,Gproblem-solving, the refusal to accept
OL,15,Gthe inevitable — these are deliberate
OL,16,Gchoices made by mission teams who
OL,17,Gunderstood that how you frame a
OL,18,Gproblem changes whether you can solve
OL,19,Git. Dementia care never got that memo.
OL,20,GThe Astronaut Protocol draws on sixty
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
